Distractor analysis:
- A: [Unconditional Support Decoy] [Inverse Support] Low-hour gardens outproducing high-hour sites contradicts the predicted labor effect.
- C: [Irrelevant Variable] [Unconditional Support Decoy] Harvest floors without hour comparisons do not test the hypothesis.
- D: [Inverse Support] [Irrelevant Variable] Soil nitrogen under fertilizer changes is outside the volunteer-hour prediction.', NULL, 'Information and Ideas', 'Command of Evidence', 'reading_writing', 'information', 'COE', NULL, 'easy', false, 'SAT', 'multiple_choice', true, true, 'scholaris_ai', '{"rw_subtype":"textual_evidence","dsat_blueprint_v1":true,"rw_format":"hypothesis_support","generator":"regenerate-english-fresh.mjs","master_manual_section":"5","english_rw_regen_v2":true,"regen_agent":"coe-master","regen_seed_offset":100000,"explanation_v2":true}'::jsonb, now(), now());
